textBeforeTable: Click on the arrow icon to sort (useful to sort by time). To help facilitate sharing a taxi if you are flying out please update the table below with the requested information. You can then see who else is departing around the same time and plan a rideshare. Take a taxi - fixed fair of $42 from the hotel to airport Take a bus - cheap but takes time, up to 2.5 hours If you are flying out of Toronto Pearson Intl then you have 2 options to get from the hotel to the airport. textAfterTable: [edit] Public Transportation The FUDCon campus location is well-served by public transit -- over 1700 vehicles a day stop at the adjacent transit loop. For more information: Toronto - TTC website - MyTTC trip planner Fares: cash fare $2.75 / 5 tokens for $11.25 / 10 tokens for $22.50 York Region, North of Toronto - including the Hilton Garden Inn hotel - YRT/VIVA Fares: cash fare $3.25 / 10 tickets for $26.00 Single tickets available from machine at Hotel stop (credit card or coins); 10-packs and single tickets available on campus (debit or cash). Probably a good idea to buy and share a 10-pack once on campus. You must purchase a single fare OR validate one fare from a 10-pack before boarding a VIVA vehicle. Fares are valid for 2 hours. Southern Ontario - GO Transit Fares vary by destination.
